type
 Meter = distinct int
 Second = distinct int
 Velocity = distinct int

proc `/`(distance: Meter, time: Second): Velocity =
 (distance.int/time.int).Velocity

let
 distance = 100.Meter
 time = 5.Second
 velocity = distance/time

import typetraits
echo velocity.type.name
